name: QANplatform
description:
QANplatform (or QAN blockchain platform)
is the Quantum-resistant hybrid blockchain platform.

QANX is the name of the utility token of QANplatform.

Build your software applications like DApps or DeFi and run business processes on blockchain
in 5 minutes with QANplatform.

Developers and enterprises can build Quantum-resistant smart-contracts, DApps, DeFi solutions, NFTs, tokens/cryptocurrencies on top of the QAN blockchain platform.
